36:11.043 --> 36:17.753
And that's a big $35 book that's 600-and-something pages with two signatures of photographs in it.

36:17.969 --> 36:20.912
And sheets, and the whole works, and a gorgeous dust jacket.

36:21.693 --> 36:25.137
And if they can put us across them, 50 cents to make a book, a dollar?

36:25.557 --> 36:26.859
Yeah, it depends on the description.

36:26.879 --> 36:28.120
Yeah, what is this, down in China?

36:28.140 --> 36:28.460
I'll bet.

36:29.041 --> 36:29.642
Yeah, probably.

36:29.662 --> 36:30.282
Singapore?

36:30.883 --> 36:33.506
Yeah.

36:33.526 --> 36:35.888
