It was fun, but they hadn't quite gotten the technology of the computer chip yet.

37:03.114 --> 37:03.655
Yeah, it goes off.

37:03.915 --> 37:04.716
You're just carrying it.

37:04.736 --> 37:05.657
It goes off, you know?

