53:42.764 --> 53:42.984
Good.

53:44.225 --> 53:49.130
I don't know if you've ever seen her do a training, but... I just met her today for the first time.

53:49.150 --> 53:49.350
Yeah.

53:50.051 --> 53:52.894
She goes... Can I keep you for one more second?

53:52.974 --> 53:53.574
Yeah.

53:53.634 --> 53:56.457
So she goes into a room of...

53:56.875 --> 54:00.118
a hundred, this is a Grand Rounds opportunity.

54:00.198 --> 54:03.080
We've kind of insinuated ourselves into this Grand Rounds.

