You don't mind if I shoot a picture, do you?

54:04.982 --> 54:05.423
Go ahead.

54:06.223 --> 54:12.649
Into this Grand Rounds opportunity, which is, you know, in medicine, that's where they teach you how to take out the appendix.

54:12.669 --> 54:14.350
Put your wallet away.

54:19.895 --> 54:25.380
So she goes in, so there's like a hundred sleepy,

54:26.221 --> 54:27.823
Yeah, fine.

