Residents, and there's like, you know, 20 grumpy attendings who are supposed to be supervising, and they're required to come to this Grand Rounds every week and learn something new.

54:40.944 --> 54:48.856
And so we've insinuated ourselves into this, you know, and so Perry is our main sort of Grand Rounds speaker.

54:49.376 --> 54:54.304
So she goes in, and you just see this room full of sleepy, tired residents.

