55:23.647 --> 55:24.829
Is she doing that around here?

55:25.670 --> 55:29.215
Those opportunities only come like 15 times a year.

55:29.275 --> 55:32.860
She probably has one on her schedule somewhere in the future.

55:32.880 --> 55:34.903
I wouldn't mind coming to one in Alaska.

55:35.244 --> 55:38.829
Yeah, but she's magical in that way.

55:39.009 --> 55:47.241
I think it's better for me to see it than to... It would be a perfect way, actually, to enter into this.

55:47.288 --> 55:49.750
I'm always thinking, how am I getting into the chapter?

55:49.950 --> 55:52.433
Well, if you could see her do a training.

