So you think you'll have one scheduled over the next couple of months?

56:07.226 --> 56:08.107
You'll have to ask her.

56:08.147 --> 56:09.348
She does her own schedule.

56:09.388 --> 56:12.031
So it's called the Grand Rounds of Training Opportunities.

